Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Black Mist
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After our class came back from the trip,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}things took a slightly strange turn\Nin our classroom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:01:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a single piece of chalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There were several pieces just this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara-no-Teika\NTraces of Beauty\NGraceful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who threw that eraser?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}LANGUAGE PREP ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone... It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}LANGUAGE PREP ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to prep the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You're on duty today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm missing my timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Timeline? Is it that scroll you always use?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The green one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. What should I do?\NIt'll be troublesome if I don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's been going on recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These incidents keep happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it just my imagination?\NShe looks like she's lost a lot of weight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to do without it.\NOh, the bell's about to ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scroll, scroll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where could that long thing have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would stand out if it had fallen on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}PING
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, I might know where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh? Ms. Kawamoto!\N- I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}WHIZ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. Now, even the black mood{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that was taking hold of the class\Nhad tried to engulf the teacher.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank goodness. Where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was mixed in with the historical timelines\Nin the social studies room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You found it for me. Thank you, Ms. Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought they all had the same shape, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brown-noser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she says,\Nbut Kawamoto is probably the one who hid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was Ms. Takagi's voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you stop muttering insults about me\Nthat are just loud enough for me to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Ms. Kawamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I was going to hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because that would be playing\Nright into your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, I hid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Ms. Kawamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Kawamoto, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, you heard what she said, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stopping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm the one who hid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not raise your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:06:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can imagine what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Ms. Takagi and her friends hid it\Nand then blamed Ms. Kawamoto, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But so what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So how am I supposed to prove it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough. I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, every single year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The students change, but every time,\Nthere's someone who gets left out and bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm just sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you have so much free time\Nto be harassing your classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Ms. Takagi, how is it\Nthat you have that much free time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop torturing your classmates\Nand study more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place,\Nwho do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Involving everyone else in your nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Think about how you're disrupting the class.\NEveryone's studying for entrance exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if a dam had burst, Teacher kept talking.\NBut her words became less articulate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After falling silent for a while...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her face darkened...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she collapsed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She never returned to school after that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was announced that\Nshe had been hospitalized due to anxiety.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? So Teacher's become a shut-in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.\NWhat's going to happen to our class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we've got entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a royal pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And like, whose fault is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, until your new homeroom teacher\Nis decided, I'll be teaching this class from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mr. Kokubu, the head teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}July 10th (Thursday)\NOn Duty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For you third-years taking\Nhigh school entrance exams soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you understand that how\Nyou spend this summer break
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will result in a turning point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate for you to have a change\Nin homeroom teachers during this period.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I heard some of you complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there was bullying so bad in here\Nthat a student transferred to another school,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, out of 38 kids,\Nno one raised their voice except certain people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the price you're paying for ignoring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, before summer vacation,\NI'd like to resolve this to some extent,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll be talking to you individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First Takagi, and then Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The new homeroom teacher's clear,\Nreasonable manner of speaking{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}made the class fall silent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you're called to stay after school,\Nreport to the faculty room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}ATTENDANCE RECORD
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, to sort out the situation,\Neach of our parents were called in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Parent-teacher-student conferences.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He asked me a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Teacher knew\Nwhat was going on the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she'd been a teacher for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the same thing\Nkept happening again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And her class would be\Nthrown into chaos every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She kept seeing situations\Nshe couldn't do anything about,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,until it reached the point\Nwhere she couldn't even get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, what should I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It went so far that\Nyou have to come in to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hina, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One cup of French toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With plenty of fresh cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Here, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}All right, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sir, I'll take two beef croquettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}One just as-is, one slathered in sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sure thing! Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}The depth of the water fluctuates.\NPlease do not step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You're always warning me\Nabout spoiling my dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get to eat what you like at a time\Nlike this, when will you eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, I'm going. Be it\Na parent-teacher conference, or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go grocery shopping\Nand then go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stew. Can I have it over my rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll put it on my rice this time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black Mist
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Light
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could I not go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go and give those selfish,\Nrotten parents a piece of my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tuesday is when you have\Nthat important catering job, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}HISS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's for an important tea party
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to celebrate the 60th anniversary\Nof Shoueidou's founding, our valued customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHOUEIDOU
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is looking forward\Nto your sweets, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know that better than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This... This is a big deal\Nfor my granddaughter, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:13:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have a good talk with her teacher,\Nso it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise it'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akari...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akari, I'm sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've put you through so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about Hina and Momo.\NThey'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'll protect them\Nfrom the both of us, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That dream again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I keep waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get my sleep.\NThe conference is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I made a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to Mom and Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Ms. Kawamoto, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Teacher!\N- Mr. Kokubu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Ueda was screwing around...\N- and broke the window with a mop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Was anyone hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Suzuki!\N- His hand is bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? What was that kid thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kawamoto, can you\Nwait in there with your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These kids are always causing trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm suddenly in charge of two classes\Nand they don't even let me catch my breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kobayashi! Go ahead of me\Nand tell everyone to stay away from the glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We'll go inside, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, for us, the most important thing\Nthis year are the high school entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I think it's better not to make any waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, going forward, if you would\Nadvise your little sister to watch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Then for us, I wouldn't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter told me\Neverything I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems your little sister has various issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I'm concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think my sister has any issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I have no idea\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No issues, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She spread rumors\Nabout my Megumi being a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does she have against my daughter?!\NThis is so upsetting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have honest conversations\Nwith your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you properly understand\Nwhat she's thinking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter is the one who's been a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard enough false accusations!\NHow low can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}WAAAAA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're clashing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I scheduled them at different times!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}RUN RUN\NHUSTLE\NHUSTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The proof that my daughter did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I can't put credence in it.\NIsn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with,\Nmy daughter says she didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Proof of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No proof? Then I think we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be okay, Mom. Leave it to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I promise to protect Hina and Momo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do? I promised her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}think of what to say...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kokubu, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My sister isn't feeling great right now,\Nso can we take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been so nervous.\NYou're as white as a sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, drink this. It'll calm you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't respond to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After I told Grandpa and Mom\Nthat it would be okay, to leave it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-After I calm down,\NI-I'll go back there once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sit down and talk to your teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That alone makes me really happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HINATA KAWAMOTO LOVES GUYS\NPERVERTED GIRL\NBITCH IDIOT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, they would never admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even think they did anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's just like with Chiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it's over and done with,\Nthey'll just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a single reason\Nto waste my life on people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll come to school to the very last day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll endure being ignored!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if they do something to me,\NI'll yell at them to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to keep my mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens here,\Nif I just survive and graduate, I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't know\Nwhere this is coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calling my Megumi a bully is a false accusation\Nof the highest order!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When there isn't even any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, there is no proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, of course there's no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ms. Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The person who does it will never admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The people around the bully know that if\Nthey snitch, they'll be the next target,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so they keep their mouths shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way proof will appear,\Nnot with bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural that there's no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only person who can say\Nthere's been bullying is the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So when Kawamoto said she was bullied,\Nthat right there is the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if that girl is lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She could say anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then where's your proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that Kawamoto is lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, where's the proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:22:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until you show me that,\Nas a representative of the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept your grievance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Kokubu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I feel better now, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.80,0:22:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Mr. Kokubu,\NI was being quite rude earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, you have nothing at all to be sorry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we talk about what to do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:37.02,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 35
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.47,0:24:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.93,0:24:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to\Nkeep calling me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.56,0:24:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.85,0:24:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, tell me what's really going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.65,0:24:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right... I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.32,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hina!\N- It's from Chiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:59.04,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ILLUSTRATION:\NHIDEAKI NISHIKAWA
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.95,0:24:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode of\N"March Comes in Like a Lion."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.78,0:24:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever I can for Hina.
